{"tid":1827962,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"避免台灣遭矮化NCC下令禁顯示「中國台灣」 陸牌手機近況超慘！","createTime":"2020-01-17T11:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T06:07:19.000Z","uid":10717,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ba92d7ff2c709cd732e14369e360104591275b3f","tid":1827962,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"去年11月，有使用中國品牌手機的民眾反映，在進行更新後，通訊紀錄從「台灣」被改為「中國台灣」。為了避免台灣遭到矮化，NCC強硬禁止手機廠牌顯示「中國台灣」並要求簽署切結書。時至今日已2個月過去了，國內的手機市場卻明顯發現中國品牌的手機一片靜悄悄，多款新機都無限期延期，恐怕銷量將嚴重受影響。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月，有華為用戶發現，手機更新後，原本台灣的標示卻變成了中國台灣，讓他忍不住打給NCC申訴，NCC調查後發現確實如此。所以NCC指出，基於維護國家尊嚴及手機主管單位立場，將採取嚴重措施，要求業者簽訂切結書，並放棄訴願及行政訴訟的權利，未來將不得再出現台灣被標為「中國台灣」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，倘若有業者違反上述的切結書內容，將依照「電信終端設備檢驗辦法」第20條第1項「電信管制射頻器材審驗辦法」或「電信管制射頻器材審驗辦法」第22條第1項規定，會撤銷手機或頻版審定證明或型式認證證明，將無法在台灣販售。<br />\n<br />\n當這項禁令一出，中國手機品牌馬上就對台灣的市場為之卻步，像是華為Mate 30 Pro取消在台上市，原先預計引入台灣的小米Note 10、realme X2 Pro都延期，至今也沒有具體上市時間，官方更沒有解釋是否是跟切結書有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過為什麼這些中國手機廠會因為這個規定、連署書而半放棄台灣市場呢？其實很簡單，有不少專家認為，若廠商簽署了NCC的切結書將捲入兩岸間的政治關係，甚至還有可能受到北京當局「關照」，自然不會輕舉妄動。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，目前僅有小米 Redmi Note 8T 與 vivo Y19 兩款陸續開賣，而號稱源於法國但背後金主實為中國的Sugar Y18則有簽署切結書，不過似乎不會對中國事業進行影響，因為他們在中國市場上沒有任何商品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de231b603339cbcfcf5916641c7a12e2de688bb","tid":1827962,"uid":233817,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"ncc 確認台灣為獨立國家, nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05653909ef7b9faa295d1f81bbbe3347c4e464c6","tid":1827962,"uid":53122,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"7de231b603339cbcfcf5916641c7a12e2de688bb","tid":1827962,"uid":233817,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"ncc 確認台灣為獨立國家, nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"ncc係台灣政府成立㗎"},{"pid":"6e36bf554731724a2318355093eba6f2d9237e7b","tid":1827962,"uid":233817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05653909ef7b9faa295d1f81bbbe3347c4e464c6","tid":1827962,"uid":53122,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"7de231b603339cbcfcf5916641c7a12e2de688bb","tid":1827962,"uid":233817,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"ncc 確認台灣為獨立國家, nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"ncc係台灣政府成立㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e115992e87919c9089d873318ecb32f61becae2","tid":1827962,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"台灣好波<br />\n台灣又贏"},{"pid":"23714f5df913be6662de40e1e080927d249c2fd5","tid":1827962,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"做得好，下一步要學支那禁寫中國台灣航空公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e3280cff9299ad22c2fc971d82cfa44e38ba3c","tid":1827962,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7de231b603339cbcfcf5916641c7a12e2de688bb","tid":1827962,"uid":233817,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"ncc 確認台灣為獨立國家, nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"寫中國台灣就唔好入黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0a7d81c97ad0cf86adf0708a22dfaf926236e2","tid":1827962,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"NCC點睇某大品牌取消台灣國旗emoji同埋台灣被回歸中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87c874487a78a81014b7132cdac6fed52c2e74a","tid":1827962,"uid":1933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4e0a7d81c97ad0cf86adf0708a22dfaf926236e2","tid":1827962,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"NCC點睇某大品牌取消台灣國旗emoji同埋台灣被回歸中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"得中港澳版先會"},{"pid":"a7213e14921b1ec23072dcbb53d280e5621cc48a","tid":1827962,"uid":3773,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"Meanwhile in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<del>Past: Hong Kong</del><br />\n<del>Yesterday: Hong Kong SAR</del><br />\nToday: Hong Kong (China)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d639ccdbd420f6fecbcae3e3aa815e1189e42521","tid":1827962,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">台灣本來就獨立<br />\n蚑那唔撚好夾硬加蚑那兩個字俾人<br />\n香港未獨立，請大家努力訓練自己體能為獨立做好準備</span></span>"},{"pid":"359fe7cb34c41d6791595918659878be941418ac","tid":1827962,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意搞埋啲小動作自我感覺良好都唔知為乜<br />\n台灣唔會係中國㗎，接受現實啦"}]}